7. Configuration

All configurations are maintained in the config.properties file.

Example:
browser=chrome
url=https://automationexercise.com
implicitWait=10
explicitWait=20

8. Reporting

* Extent Reports are used for test execution reporting
* Reports are generated in the reports folder
* Screenshots are attached for failed test cases

9. Screenshots

* Screenshots are captured automatically on test failure
* Stored in the screenshots folder

 10. Execution Steps

1. Clone the repository
2. Import the project as a Maven project
3. Run testng.xml

11. Key Features

* Page Object Model implementation
* Data-driven testing using Excel
* Screenshot capture on failure
* Structured and reusable framework
* Easy to extend and maintain

 12. Conclusion

This automation framework is designed to be scalable, maintainable, and reusable.
It successfully automates key functionalities of the application and fulfills the project requirements.
